<a href="/articles/26512.html" class="com-grid-article" >
	<div class="grid-article-hd">
		<img class="pic lazyload" data-src="/system/articles/articleshows/26512/indexMediumPc2/26512.jpg?1462516975" alt="伟大的人值得穿好点，爱因斯坦、达尔文都被吐槽了">
		
		<p class="category">
			<img src="/system/categories/iconwhites/18/medium/18.png?1411569398" alt="商业">
			<span>商业</span>
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">伟大的人值得穿好点，爱因斯坦、达尔文都被吐槽了</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-ft  clearfix">
		<span class="smart-date" data-originDate="2016-05-06 18:04:04 +0800"></span>
		<div class="ribbon">
